OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FSome sunshine will develop
OL,6,Fon Saturday morning, though cloud is
OL,7,Fset to increase from the north into
OL,8,Fthe afternoon, with some showery rain
OL,9,Fdeveloping. Still warm, though rather
OL,10,Fbreezy.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FSunday
OL,13,Fwill be a fresher, still breezy day
OL,14,Fwith sunshine and scattered showers.
OL,15,FSome sunshine at times early next week
OL,16,Ftoo, though some patchy rain is also
OL,17,Fpossible.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
